<category term="Ahl al-Hadith - Salafiyyah &amp; What Opposes It" scheme="https://forum.salafiri.com/viewforum.php?f=40" label="Ahl al-Hadith - Salafiyyah &amp; What Opposes It"/>
<content type="html" xml:base="https://forum.salafiri.com/viewtopic.php?t=1561&amp;p=1680#p1680"><![CDATA[
The Salaf us-Saleh Spilt Their Blood for this Ummah, You Wasted Their Bleeding in Vain. <br />Part 3<br /><br />They say:<br /><strong>These ‘Aqīdah issues become secondary, I don't care what anyone says...</strong><br /><br />Shaykh Sāleh b. al-Fawzān was asked:<br /><br /><blockquote class="uncited"><div><br />“Is entry into Paradise or the Fire dependent upon the soundness or correct Manhaj?” he answered and said: “Yes, if the Manhaj is sound, the person will be from amongst the people of Paradise since he will be upon the Manhaj of the Messenger Sallalahu Alayhi Wasalam and the Manhaj of the Salaf us-Saleh. He will be from the people of Paradise by the permission of Allāh. If he traverses a misguided or deviant methodology, then he will be an innovator in the fire. So the soundness of Manhaj or a lack thereof -  determines a person's entry into Paradise or the Fire.” (Ajwibātul Mufīdah, 77)<br /></div></blockquote><br /><br />Benefit<br />The Muslim must also focus on the deviant calls and methodologies, which have crept into Islam due to the preaching of the ignorant callers, who base their da'wah on emotion, popular culture, popularity and “like” contests. The aim is to achieve Paradise through the worship of Allāh alone without any partners. We should focus on rejecting falsehood, which has crippled the progression of Islam. Likewise, and more importantly, we should make inkār of innovated methodologies and innovators. This includes all methodologies which oppose the truth and lead to the Fire. May Allāh save us from such a torment, Amīn<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="https://forum.salafiri.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=48">AbuKhuzaimahAnsari</a> — Fri Jul 19, 2019 9:46 pm</p><hr />
]]></content>
