<entry>
<author><name><![CDATA[AbuKhuzaimahAnsari]]></name></author>
<updated>2019-07-19T21:46:05+01:00</updated>
<published>2019-07-19T21:46:05+01:00</published>
<id>https://forum.salafiri.com/viewtopic.php?t=1561&amp;p=1679#p1679</id>
<link href="https://forum.salafiri.com/viewtopic.php?t=1561&amp;p=1679#p1679"/>
<title type="html"><![CDATA[Ahl al-Hadith - Salafiyyah &amp; What Opposes It • Re: Comments on Muhammad Hijabs Views on Unity and Cooperation on Self Understood Maslaha]]></title>

<category term="Ahl al-Hadith - Salafiyyah &amp; What Opposes It" scheme="https://forum.salafiri.com/viewforum.php?f=40" label="Ahl al-Hadith - Salafiyyah &amp; What Opposes It"/>
<content type="html" xml:base="https://forum.salafiri.com/viewtopic.php?t=1561&amp;p=1679#p1679"><![CDATA[
The Salaf us-Saleh Spilt Their Blood for this Ummah, You Wasted Their Bleeding in Vain. <br />Part 2<br /><br />They say:<br /><strong>I don't give a damn, give me the knowledge. If they have a skill set, we will bring them in, we don't care who they are…</strong><br /><br />Shaykh Sāleh b. al-Fawzān said:<br /><br /><blockquote class="uncited"><div><br />“So it is obligatory upon everyone who has knowledge and insight, to make the danger clear of these groups and parties, which have cropped up in the name of “Da'wah to Islam” while many of their members, and even their leaders do not know the reality of Islam or what negates and breaks or reduces it and they do not possess the pre-requisites for calling to it.”<br /></div></blockquote><br /><br />(From Shaykh al-Fawzān's introduction to Shaykh al-Suhaymi's, Tanbih ‘Ulul Absār Ilā Kamāl al-Dīn WaMā Fī’l Bid'ah Minal Akhtār, page f)<br /><br />Benefit<br />Lacking knowledge, coupled with a hyperactive mindset, is indeed a recipe for disaster. Being ignorant of the essentials and basic reality of Islam will cause confusion, moreso when individuals put themselves at the forefront of da'wah. One could possibly convince himself if the da'wah was limited to general da'wah, but when they incoherently push into the fundamentals and principles of Ahl al-Sunnah and Salafiyyah, while recklessly opposing and challenging it, they need to be stopped, educated and reprimanded for their crime against the Salafi Manhaj.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="https://forum.salafiri.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=48">AbuKhuzaimahAnsari</a> — Fri Jul 19, 2019 9:46 pm</p><hr />
]]></content>
