Comments on Muhammad Hijabs Views on Unity and Cooperation on Self Understood Maslaha<br />The Salaf us-Saleh Spilt Their Blood for this Ummah, You Wasted Their Bleeding in Vain. <br />Part 1<br /><br />They say:<br /><strong>I don't give a damn, give me the knowledge. If they have a skill set, we will bring them in, we don't care who they are…</strong><br /><br />Imām Ibn ‘Abd Barr (d.463H) said over 977 years ago, concerning the Hadīth of Ka'b b. Mālik RadiAllahu Anhu when he remained behind from the expedition of Tabūk:<br /><br /><blockquote class="uncited"><div><br />“The following may be derived from the Hadith of Ka'b: proof that it is permissible for a man to abandon his brother when an innovation or sin appear in him, with the hope that such abandonment of him leads to reprimanding or disciplining him, through it's admonishment of him.” (Al-Tamhīd Limā Fi'l Muwattā‘ Minal Ma'anī wa'l Asānīd Fī Ahādīth Rasūlillāh, 6:118)<br /></div></blockquote><br />Benefit<br />Ahl al-Sunnah, the Salafis or the Ahl al-Hadith have history, a heritage, a path and methodology from  approximately over 1000 years. Your history is 1872 legislation of the British Parliament, and even that is contradictory to what you claim you stand for, i.e. divide and conquer, while hiding behind democracy of the colonial imperialists, who slaughtered, captured, terrorised and killed millions of Muslims.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="https://forum.salafiri.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=48">AbuKhuzaimahAnsari</a> — Fri Jul 19, 2019 9:45 pm</p><hr />
